usastats_querye.Rd

usastats_querye - convenient way to see US mean, pctiles of ENVIRONMENTAL indicators in lookup table

Usage

usastats_querye(varnames = EJAM::names_e, PCTILES = NULL, dig = 4)

Arguments

varnames

names of columns in lookup table, like "proximity.rmp"

PCTILES

vector of percentiles 0-100 and/or "mean"

dig

how many digits to round to

Examples
